# The Movie Database (TMDB) API — powers all the HD artwork, trailers and cast.
# 1. Create a free account at https://www.themoviedb.org/
# 2. Go to Settings -> API and request a v3 API key (instant approval).
# 3. Copy this file to `.env.local` and paste your key below, then restart `npm start`.
#
# Without a key the app still runs on a bundled local catalogue.
REACT_APP_TMDB_KEY=your_tmdb_v3_api_key_here
